{"title":"刘公岛","authors":["时焕年"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘公岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时焕年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"码头咫尺，缆绳待抛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一瞬间的期待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子把岁月拖老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对峙终于疲惫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任白云悠悠，情牵梦绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是你不思故土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是你无力停靠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那枚鱼雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你和邓世昌获得永生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对迷惘和痛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你重新聚敛忠魂的热望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一腔爱恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给知情的海涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，当东部士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在晨光中站起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才品味到真正的自豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔涌的海，飞溅的浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起太阳的微笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启航吧，古老而崭新的战舰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着五洲宾朋，中外游客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶向天涯海角。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}